  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Safe and Clean Water for Mafwasa Community</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will sink 3 boreholes for 325 households who draw water from unprotected shallow wells, rivers and streams. It will result in reduced incidences of waterborne related diseases, and will further reduce time and energy expended - especially by women and girls who are traditionally responsible for fetching water. The project will therefore contribute to the wellbeing of children and their families.</narrative>
  </description>
